{"title":"塞外集","authors":["巴牧"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":6,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞外集"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借问南风几时来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边塞云散天如海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借问南风几时来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞北稻花等待开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借问南风几时来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北国土地需要阳光晒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借问南风几时来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年活计塞北人早安排。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！问春春不知，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问柳柳摇摆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见呢喃燕子笑语飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在同劲风比高矮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笛声来自白云间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山高顶天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上云成堆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上羊成团。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远看——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊在天空跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云绕山腰转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，真奇观，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧人一曲歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笛声来自白云端。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}